PlayerInformationFileInterpreter - Class in files
Utility class which creates a reader and interpreter to read and then interpret the data from a file whose filename is passed via the constructor.
PlayerInformationFileInterpreter(String) - Constructor for class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
At instantiation this immediately creates and executes, in sequence, both a reader and interpreter which will immediately read the file specified by the filename at instantiation, store the data in a string array, interpret the stored data based on the format of specified for "Player Information Files", and, upon the completion of instantiation, allow access to the interpreted data though several getter methods.
